    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken incredible care of it, keeping it garaged and spotless, so it's still in that perfect, like-new condition you've been searching for. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
